"https://secure.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/wiki/Ali_Khamenei")和突尼西亞最近被趕下台的總統[宰因．阿比丁．本．阿里](https://secure.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/wiki/Zine_El_Abidine_Ben_Ali
